# Warwick Data Analytics MSc 2025/26

This repository showcases my work as a Data Analytics MSc student at the University of Warwick (2025/26).

It highlights my ability to:
- Analyse complex datasets
- Build machine learning models
- Extract insights for decision-making
- Communicate findings through clear visualisations

Projects in this repository reflect both academic coursework and independent exploration, demonstrating my interest in applying data analytics to real-world problems.

I aim to continuously improve my analytical thinking, technical skills, and problem-solving ability throughout this programme.